": "If I make a deal with Iran, it will be a good and proper one, not like the one made by Obama, which gave Iran massive amounts of CASH, and a clear and open path to a Nuclear Weapon. Our deal is the exact opposite, but nobody has seen it, or knows what it is. It isn\u2019t even fully negotiated yet. So don\u2019t listen to the losers, who are critical about something they know nothing about. Unlike those before me who should have solved this problem many years ago, I don\u2019t make bad deals! President DJT", "large_image": "N7GMXoS8RfbbxAn9.png", "title": "Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump)"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsZF0pov", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 65, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "retard", "id": 8638921, "raw_content": "", "author": "TEXinLA", "created": 1779715013479, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Valiazaner", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.zerohedge.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsZF0pov.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.zerohedge.com/political/colbert-blames-trump-massive-profit-losses-killed-his-show", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Colbert Blames Trump, But Massive Profit Losses Killed His Show", "last_comment_created": 1779727725217, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 65, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "ZeroHedge - On a long enough timeline, the survival rate for everyone drops to zero", "large_image": "mRTUsB7EPhBseS2O.png", "title": "Colbert Blames Trump, But Massive Profit Losses Killed His Show"}, "post_flair_text": "RETARD", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsZF0pt6", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 64, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8638934, "raw_content": "Very simply these two did not represent the wishes of the people who elected them and are therefore being replaced.\n\nCoaches lose jobs.  Quarterbacks lose jobs.  Mechanics lose jobs.  Accountants lose jobs.  It's a normal process that actually contributes to economic growth.\n\nPeople have choices.  Teams have choices.  Customers have choices.  And, VOTERS HAVE CHOICES!\n\nThe absolute arrogance of these two are perfect indication of why they will no longer be there.  \n\nTheir ultimate arrogance....\"The People are Stupid for Replacing Me!\"\n\nIt's never, I failed.  Not with them.\n\n", "author": "dataonly", "created": 1779715297154, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Inukshuk", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Thom Tillis and Bill Cassidy Despicable Behavior on the Way out the Door", "last_comment_created": 1779729221488, "content": "<p>Very simply these two did not represent the wishes of the people who elected them and are therefore being replaced.</p>\n<p>Coaches lose jobs.  Quarterbacks lose jobs.  Mechanics lose jobs.  Accountants lose jobs.  It's a normal process that actually contributes to economic growth.</p>\n<p>People have choices.  Teams have choices.  Customers have choices.  And, VOTERS HAVE CHOICES!</p>\n<p>The absolute arrogance of these two are perfect indication of why they will no longer be there.</p>\n<p>Their ultimate arrogance....&quot;The People are Stupid for Replacing Me!&quot;</p>\n<p>It's never, I failed.  Not with them.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 64, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsZF0qHr", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 55, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8638993, "raw_content": "", "author": "Royall", "created": 1779718205381, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "zooty", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsZF0qHr.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/GkPI9hbl5NcT.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/MQQFAxtcfm4ru7ya.jpeg", "width": 768, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 473}], "blurhash": "UKE{IyXr0Y}%x_s;NGWU9^oHwbNbxuo#s:WD", "full_resolution": [578, 939]}, "title": "Kaja Kallas - \"If we stop supporting Ukraine, we are effectively supporting Russia.\u201d\n\nEU leaders are blackmailing everyone to supporting Ukraine.\nBut I believe President Trump won't support their money laundering scheme.", "last_comment_created": 1779721276986, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 3, "score_up": 55, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""},